Text: Got this program off scenereleases a bit ago, as I have a pretty wicked trojan infestation.  First off, the keygen doesn't generate valid serials, nor does the bruteforcer option work.  The program locked up my computer to the point of having to force a restart when I ran a scan.  Even the UNINSTALL process crashed when it ran.  Don't bother with this program.. look elsewhere.

Keygen doesn't generate useful serials

Not stable
